These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, lime, onion, peas
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, pakistani, polish, argentine
1. the pakistani is on the left of the brazilian##1
2. the person eating watermelon is the argentine##1
3. the polish is on the right of the brazilian##1
4. the person eating lime is on the left of the argentine##1
5. the person eating peas is on the left of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | peas | onion | lime | watermelon   |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | brazilian     | polish   | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, singing, gardening, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, basketball, tennis, climbing
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | gardening | dancing | singing | chess    |
| Sport   | tennis    | basketball      | golf | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, gardening, baking, skydiving
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, martial-arts, romance, documentary
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | dancing | skydiving | baking   | gardening |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller   | romance | documentary | martial-arts         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, animation, family, documentary
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, baseball, parkour, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is baseball is the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | animation | musical  | family      |
| Sport         | baseball | snowboarding   | parkour | lacrosse |

