.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, orange, carrot, radish
4 different pets are kept: lizard, guinea-pig, frog, rat
1. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
3. the person eating radish is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | radish | carrot | orange | pumpkin |
| Pet    | lizard       | rat | frog | guinea-pig     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, colombian, french, malaysian
4 different pets are kept: cat, horse, lizard, bird
1. the colombian is on the far right##1
2. the malaysian is on the left of the french##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the french##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | malaysian | french | brazilian | colombian |
| Pet           | cat      | lizard | bird | horse    |

