.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, house, metal, jazz
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake, hamster, lizard
1. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
3. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the far right##1
5. the fan of house is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | metal | house | funk | jazz  |
| Pet           | hamster | hedgehog | lizard       | snake |

