.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, dancer, coach, manager
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, train, bike, ship
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the dancer##1
2. the person driving the ship is the manager##1
3. the dancer is on the right of the scientist##1
4. the coach is on the left of the person driving the train##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | coach | scientist      | dancer | manager |
| Transport   | taxi          | train | bike     | ship    |

