2. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation    | epic       | action | western   |
