.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, 7up, soy-milk, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, van, scooter, motorbike
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the van is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | fanta | soy-milk  | 7up | tea |
| Transport   | motorbike | scooter | van          | roller    |

