.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, 7up, soy-milk, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, pop, salsa, funk
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking 7up is the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | 7up  | lemonade | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | salsa | funk           | pop   |

