3. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | water   | sprite | lemonade   | hot-chocolate      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | horror      | documentary | time-travel |

