2. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | reading | board-games | hiking |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | mystery    | superhero      | zombie   |

