.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, russian, malaysian, chinese
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, train, motorbike, ship
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the russian##1
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the polish is on the left of the malaysian##1
4. the chinese is the person driving the ship##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the left of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | polish | malaysian | russian | chinese   |
| Transport     | motorbike  | roller    | train       | ship |

 